          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Angles of Irradiation of the Target by Deuteruim Ion",
                " Beam are 0, 30, 60, 90, 120 and 130 Degrees. Effective",
